      "duration": 1.69,
      "size": 27072,
      "text": "平面上散布着成千上万个点，给你一个新位置。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kd-tree",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kd-tree/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "要找出离它最近的那个点，逐个比较当然可以，但太慢了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kd-tree",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kd-tree/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.71,
      "size": 27360,
      "text": "KD 树用一种巧妙的切分，让这件事快得多。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kd-tree",
      "section_id": "axis",
      "line_id": "axis-1",
      "filename": "axis-axis-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kd-tree/xiaoxiao/axis-axis-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.69,
      "size": 27072,
      "text": "第一层，我们竖着切一刀，把点分成左右两半。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kd-tree",
      "section_id": "axis",
      "line_id": "axis-2",
      "filename": "axis-axis-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kd-tree/xiaoxiao/axis-axis-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "第二层，改成横着切一刀，把点分成上下两半。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kd-tree",
      "section_id": "axis",
      "line_id": "axis-3",
      "filename": "axis-axis-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kd-tree/xiaoxiao/axis-axis-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "就这样竖、横、竖、横地交替下去，平面被层层划分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kd-tree",
      "section_id": "build",
      "line_id": "build-1",
      "filename": "build-build-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kd-tree/xiaoxiao/build-build-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.44,
      "size": 23040,
      "text": "每一刀都切在当前坐标的中位数点上。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kd-tree",
      "section_id": "build",
      "line_id": "build-2",
      "filename": "build-build-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kd-tree/xiaoxiao/build-build-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "中位数保证两边点数几乎相等，树就变得平衡。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kd-tree",
      "section_id": "build",
      "line_id": "build-3",
      "filename": "build-build-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kd-tree/xiaoxiao/build-build-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.74,
      "size": 27792,
      "text": "平衡的树只有大约 log n 层，查询自然更快。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kd-tree",
      "section_id": "prune",
      "line_id": "prune-1",
      "filename": "prune-prune-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kd-tree/xiaoxiao/prune-prune-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "查询时先扎进查询点所在的那一侧，快速找到一个候选最近点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kd-tree",
      "section_id": "prune",
      "line_id": "prune-2",
      "filename": "prune-prune-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kd-tree/xiaoxiao/prune-prune-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.31,
      "size": 37008,
      "text": "再看另一侧：如果切分线比当前最近距离还远，就整块跳过。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kd-tree",
      "section_id": "prune",
      "line_id": "prune-3",
      "filename": "prune-prune-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kd-tree/xiaoxiao/prune-prune-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "这一步剪枝砍掉了大量无用比较，这正是效率的关键。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kd-tree",
      "section_id": "interaction",
